comments: Williams (OKC) does not establish legal guarding position in Embiid's (PHI) path prior to body contact occurring that affects Embiid's shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) gathers the ball on his left foot, establishing his right as his pivot, which he maintains.
Melton (PHI) grabs and pulls Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) jersey away from his body while drawn into the air on Gilgeous-Alexander's pump fake, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Williams (OKC) steps out of bounds on the sideline while in contact with the ball.

Replay review of the foul called on Embiid (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Embiid cleanly blocks the ball prior to it reaching its apex and incidental follow-through body contact occurs with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) during his driving shot attempt. As no team had possession at the time of the whistle, play correctly resumes with a jump ball at center circle.
Joe (OKC) attempts to tie the ball up in Melton's (PHI) hands, and marginal contact occurs with Melton's arms.
Melton (PHI) switches his pivot foot before passing.
Williams (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position and incidental foot-to-foot contact occurs with Embiid (PHI) that dislodges him from his position.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Joe (OKC) closes-out toward Maxey (PHI) and initiates body contact that affects Maxey's jump shot attempt.
Melton's (PHI) arm is briefly in Joe's (OKC) path before he retracts it and marginal contact occurs during the in-bound play.
Batum (PHI) moves alongside Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) commits a take foul on Melton (PHI).
Embiid (PHI) does not maintain a legal guarding position as he extends his hand into Bertans' (OKC) body while he is airborne on his jump shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Williams (OKC) attempts to tie the ball up in Melton's (PHI) hands and marginal contact occurs with Melton's right arm.
Wiggins (OKC) commits a take foul on Batum (PHI).
Williams (OKC) initiates contact by grabbing Harris' (PHI) left arm prior to Harris' left arm extension in the backcourt. A personal foul should have been assessed.
Giddey (OKC) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Joe (OKC) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Batum (PHI) establishes himself in a legal position out of bounds with his right foot prior to releasing the inbounds pass.
Holmgren (OKC) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
